Only tube-and-wing configurations were considered. In an effort to reduce the cross section and wetted area, the absolute minimum fuselage dimensions were defined first: 19 passengers were seated two abreast (30′′\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
